### 🟡 Medium

---

#### 6. Server Listens on All Interfaces (OWASP A05 – Security Misconfiguration)

**Line 18** — `app.listen(3000)` binds to `0.0.0.0` by default, exposing the service on every network interface, including external ones.

```js
