### 🔴 Critical

#### 1. Broken Access Control — Unauthenticated PII Exposure (OWASP A01)

The `/users` endpoint returns personally identifiable information (names and email addresses) with **zero authentication or authorization**. Anyone who can reach the server can enumerate all users.

```js
